data.description:
Experience the charm of this exquisite home situated in the sought-after Farrington subdivision, offering a picturesque North-facing view. This splendid single-family residence comprises five bedrooms and four full baths. The main level presents an inviting open-concept design, seamlessly connecting the kitchen, breakfast nook, and living room. Gleaming hardwood floors grace the kitchen, dining room, and hallways, enhancing the overall elegance.

Ascending to the second floor reveals the primary suite, accompanied by three additional bedrooms, a loft, and a sizable bonus room ideal for either entertaining or creating a home office. To further elevate the possibilities, venture downstairs to the unfinished basement, where the potential is limitless. Don't let this opportunity slip away – transform this house into your dream home!
